  <section class="oc-features" aria-labelledby="oc-features-title">
    <div class="oc-section-label"><span>⟩</span> What It Does</div>
    <div class="oc-feature-grid">
      <article class="oc-card oc-feature">
        <div class="oc-feature-icon">💻</div>
        <h3>Runs on Your Machine</h3>
        <p>Mac, Windows, or Linux. Anthropic, OpenAI, or local models. Private by default.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="oc-card oc-feature">
        <div class="oc-feature-icon">💬</div>
        <h3>Any Chat App</h3>
        <p>WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord, Slack, Signal, or iMessage.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="oc-card oc-feature">
        <div class="oc-feature-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>Persistent Memory</h3>
        <p>Remembers you and becomes uniquely yours. Your preferences, your context, your AI.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="oc-card oc-feature">
        <div class="oc-feature-icon">🌐</div>
        <h3>Browser Control</h3>
        <p>Browse the web, fill forms, and extract data from any site.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="oc-card oc-feature">
        <div class="oc-feature-icon">⌘</div>
        <h3>Full System Access</h3>
        <p>Read and write files, run shell commands, execute scripts. Full access or sandboxed.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="oc-card oc-feature">
        <div class="oc-feature-icon">🧩</div>
        <h3>Skills &amp; Plugins</h3>
        <p>Extend with community skills or build your own. It can even write its own.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

